HEADWORD: Trucker
<hw>Truck"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who trucks; a
trafficker.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>No man having ever yet driven a saving bargain with this great
<qex>trucker</qex> for souls.</q> <rj><qau>South.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
